{"word":"G5052 - τελεσφορέω - telesphoréō - tel-es-for-eh'-o - Bring fruit to perfection","slug":"G5052","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τελεσφορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>telesphoréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tel-es-for-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bring fruit to perfection"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x03C3;&#x03C6;&#x03BF;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - telesphoreo&#x0304;</b> - <i>tel-es-for-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5056\">G5056</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342\">G5342</a>; to <i>be a bearer to completion</i> (maturity), that is, to <i>ripen</i> fruit (figuratively): - bring fruit to perfection."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2005\">G2005</a>, <a href=\"#/G3838\">G3838</a>, <a href=\"#/G4930\">G4930</a>, <a href=\"#/G4931\">G4931</a>, <a href=\"#/G5046\">G5046</a>, <a href=\"#/G5047\">G5047</a>, <a href=\"#/G5048\">G5048</a>, <a href=\"#/G5049\">G5049</a>, <a href=\"#/G5050\">G5050</a>, <a href=\"#/G5051\">G5051</a>, <a href=\"#/G5055\">G5055</a>, <a href=\"#/G5056\">G5056</a>"}]}